<p>
<i>Footnotes:</i><br />
<span style="font-size: smaller;">(1) The decision rules are based on WHO recommendations and may vary from country to country and within regions of the same country depending on national and local vaccination policies.<br /> 
(2) Based on WHO recommendations found on WHO and other related websites on July 7th, 2009 and subjected to change at any time.<br />
(3) This demo is supposed to act as a technical example of the implementation of decision support systems using OSHIP and should never be used as a decision-making tool for the vaccination recommendation of real cases.</span>
